name: Black Orca Mermaid
description:
Originated on Kalamint as an inspirational mash up of swimming, charity, and a Black future.

If you found and hold this token, expect music and airdrops in the future. Make your way over to Kalamint to see the early hand drawings, the story, and #thepencils that inspired this animated sound filled illustration. 

Featuring "Universe" the original instrumental by QueenEarth.
